Package: agentr
Type: Package
Title: Cognitive Core for Agentic Workflows in R
Version: 0.2.4.2
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Oliver", 
           family = "Zhou",
           email = "oliver.yxzhou@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: 
    Cognitive and human-interaction core for intelligent-agent scaffolding.
    The package represents agent state, supports human-in-the-loop scaffolding,
    and now centers agent-spec design with workflow specifications kept as a
    nested planning artifact. It intentionally excludes communication backends
    and provider-specific LLM client code so that reasoning, design, and
    execution transport remain cleanly separated.
